title: Marilyn Manson - Ultimate Rare Tracks FLAC
description:
Marilyn Manson - RARE TRACKS

I guarantee you that this is the best collection of Marilyn Manson material you will find out there . 
Out of the 117 tracks included here 104 tracks are in FLAC and 13 tracks are in MP3 because I couldn't find higher quality versions. 
I felt it was time someone compiled this material in the best possible quality. 
This has taken me a considerable amount of time to get together. 
Some of the material I had in my own collection, but for many tracks I had to hunt them down at the library or by sifting throught countless old torrents from various websites. 
I would like to thank mansonwiki.com for providing me with all the information that I needed to get this together.
I would also like to thank anybody that has ever uploaded any rare Manson on here or any of the other torrent sites out there. 
This collection should be 99% complete right up until Holy Wood/Golden Age because I really lost interest in Manson after that.
If anybody has anything I don't have here or has it in better quality please let me know.

Enjoy!
Snakeeyedsissy
